; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.6; padding-right: 0px\">理财新时期，还需要更多的冷静和思考。民众对于理财，已经熟悉不过。这水是深不可测。股市熔断两次洗礼，蒸发几万亿。市场兴起的互联网金融，更让人恐惧不安。总之，中国的理财市场是不断被洗礼和重塑的过程。没有风雨，怎能见彩虹呢？这也是必经的道路吧。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">从去年接触中国艺交所邮币卡电子交易，试手两三月，赔是肯定的，赚是妄想<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.6; padding-right: 0px\">的。要说经验嘛，也谈不上造诣，更扯不到研究，只是一种个人的心得。但对于邮币卡交易的未来，信心百倍。毕竟，相对于其他理财而言，邮币卡电子交易更加安全可靠。我也把邮币卡电子交易常常作为一种理念新领域进行理性的推崇。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans