webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 24px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 343px; width: 490px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031225033.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 24px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51,51,51); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 24px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 28px\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">在今天冷热不均的新理财时期，理财产品又层出不穷，那么作为邮币卡电子交易这一新品种，如何看待和介入呢？</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">所谓<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">邮币卡电子盘</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">就是把传统的需要在也包括交易市场交易的交易模式转变为电子化交易模式，投资者从买卖象征邮币卡实物的所有权，通过<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">T+0</strong>操作模式，从中获利。</span>从2015年8月26日，中国艺交所由币卡电子交易平台正式上线以来，截止目前已经有28个品种在线交易。未来市场驱动之下，将会有更多的品种出现在交易盘面。这为更多的理财者，提供广阔的理财选择空间。</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 446px; width: 503px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031226024.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">如何看待？</strong>对于林林总总的理财产品，已经让人目不暇接。而邮币卡电子交易相对于其他理财产品，更为安全可靠。安全可靠在于机构本身的权威性，也在于平台操作模式的灵活性，即时买入、即时卖出、即时止损的T+0模式，还在于资金出入方便。T+0模式可以在当天进行无数次的交易，这为投资理财者也提供了尽情展示技能的舞台和空间。试想一下，如果在众多的理财产品面前，你是选择有官方背景、有权威机构的产品，还是选择那些民间的产品呢？至少在保障方面，民众更倾向于政府。</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">如何介入？</strong>方便的很。介入资金可大可小，没有约束，只要能够购买一枚，也即二三十元到上百上千上万元皆可。操作流程入下：</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: medium; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">投资人会员开户流程</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: medium; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 608px; width: 489px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031229007.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: medium; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">除此之外，你还可以成为居间商，即<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">经纪会员，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\">其开户流程如下：</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 559px; width: 472px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031229046.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">牛羊岂是圈中物，一旦遇风便成精。</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">至所以拟这样的题目，是因为盘中有二轮牛套票、二轮羊套票和兔年流通币。在前期鼎盛时期的盘面中，牛羊兔高位横盘，价格不菲。后期随邮币卡盘面下行，到目前位置已经到了可以介入操作的时期。从近日开始，盘面介入资金量上升，品种纷纷走稳上扬，空间开始放量。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">什么是二轮牛套票和二轮羊套票呢？那么我们就拿牛羊来说一下藏品的特点：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">藏品特点之二轮牛套票：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 546px; width: 641px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031230041.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">这套丁丑年邮票为我国发行的第二轮生肖邮票的第6套。在9套参加评审的方案中，我国年轻的邮票雕刻师呼振源一举中标，尽管两枚邮票分别采用剪纸、年画两种不同的艺术手法，但设计者已充分考虑到它们之间色彩的协调性和统一性，造型大方稳健，民族风格浓郁，线条粗犷，刀法细腻，色彩斑斓，具有强烈的装饰韵味和艺术感染力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp;生肖，是全球华人共有的人生密码和文化纽带，中国对生肖有特殊的情感寄托，集邮爱好者对收集生肖票也有特殊的偏好，广泛的受众形成了庞大的市场。生肖邮票对于中国邮市来说，好像菜里的盐般，不可或缺，一直担任着邮市风向的重要角色。二轮生肖牛版票，包含&ldquo;金牛奋蹄&rdquo;和&ldquo;牛耕年丰&rdquo;各一版，以一字一画的形式，完整演绎了&ldquo;牛&rdquo;这深受国人喜爱的动物形象，自发行之日起，就成为邮市热点品种。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">藏品特点之二轮羊套票：</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 457px; width: 604px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031231035.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span></strong></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">国家邮政局定于2003年1月5日发行《癸未年》特种邮票1套2枚。2003年是农历癸未年，即羊年。羊在中国的传统装饰中应用很广，古人把羊与祥通用。大吉羊即为大吉祥。用羊装饰图案就有吉利、祥瑞的意义。癸未年生肖邮票的第一枚选用陕西凤翔县民间传统的泥玩具为主图。此玩具造型生动、可爱、色彩饱满艳丽，以代表喜庆的红色为主调，衬托出浓郁的吉祥气氛，昂首前行的这只羊显得朝气蓬勃，给人一往无前的启示。第二枚邮票图案采用剪纸形式，将两只羊和汉字楷书&ldquo;羊&rdquo;组合为一体，构成&ldquo;三羊&rdquo;的图形，寓意&ldquo;三阳开泰&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">生肖羊&mdash;&mdash;被誉为生肖邮票的&ldquo;回头羊&rdquo;。2003年第二轮生肖邮票羊票的设计采用了中国的腊梅、牡丹、荷花、菊花四季吉祥花卉，有美感，也符合羊大为美的内涵。生肖羊邮票也被称之为&ldquo;回头羊&rdquo;，是对整个一轮生肖票的回顾，也是对过去十二年中国发展的回顾，具有极高的收藏意义。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">这就是牛羊套票的特点。标题借用了&ldquo;鲤鱼岂是池中物&rdquo;的典故，来进一步说明邮币卡电子交易的可介入性和可操作性，以及长期参与的理性信知。在最后，还是让我们认知一下中国艺交所邮币卡交易中心的属性吧！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"height: 191px; width: 662px\" src=\"/upload/201603/201603031232043.jpg\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(123,12,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">2015年8月26日</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">中国工艺艺术品交易所有限公司邮币卡交易中心是由国务院国资委所属中央企业&mdash;&mdash;中国工艺（集团）公司联合中国文联所属中联国际文化发展有限公司、北京工美集 团有限责任公司发起成立的，是唯一一家获证监会牵头的&ldquo;清理整顿各类交易场所部际联席会议&rdquo;批准入市的&ldquo;中国&rdquo;字号艺术品现货商品交易所。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172,57,255); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding-top: 0px; font: 16px/25px \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">中国艺交所邮币卡交易中心的成立，融合了互联网和金融的优势，切实落实国家大力打造互联网+经济的战略部署，将互联网、金融和文化完美的结合在一起，为广大收藏爱好者和投资者提供了一个公开、公正、公平、透明的收藏品现货商品交易平台。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">邮币卡交易中心的定位：作为全国首家邮票、钱币等收藏品&ldquo;中国&rdquo;字号实物挂牌交易中心，将建设成中国邮票、钱币等收藏品交易领域的权威平台，成为全国邮票、钱币等收藏市场价格的风向标。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">展望未来，交易中心还将进一步丰富自身的业务范围，为广大客户提供更多的、更规范的金融服务项目，诸如：邮币卡藏品集散中心、邮币卡托管交收中心、文化收藏品类理财中心、邮币卡市场研究院、学术交流中心和会展中心等。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; white-space: normal; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\" />\r\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Simsun; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 60px; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255)\">中国艺交所将忠实履行中央企业的社会责任，全力打造国家重点邮币卡电子交易所，为弘扬中华文化、振兴文化产业做出应有贡献，为把中国建设成世界重要的艺术品、文化收藏品交易中心做出应有努力！</span></span></p>',1,'2016-03-03 12:41:25','2021-01-22 01:09:21',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2016-03-03 00:41:25');
